## Command cheat-sheet

| Action                          | Command                    |
| ------------------------------- | -------------------------- |
| Status                          | `git status`               |
| Stage                           | `git add [files]`          |
| Commit                          | `git commit -m "[message]"` |
| Push branch                     | `git push origin [branch]` |
| Pull branch                     | `git pull origin [branch]` |
| Undo last commit, keep changes  | `git reset --soft HEAD~1`  |

